primary.request: Check address and ownership on file
primary.context: Caller had questions regarding a maintenance bill and wanted to verify account details.
primary.detail: The AI successfully verified the caller and provided the address and owner name on file.

steps: Caller stated they had questions about a bill.
AI identified it as a maintenance bill and initiated account lookup via phone number.
Caller asked for the address on file; AI provided it.
Caller asked for the owner name on file; AI provided it.
Caller confirmed no further assistance was needed.

clarifications.note: AI asked for spelling after name mismatch

actions.detail: Verified name Valerie Creo and state New Jersey

insights.summary: The caller wanted to verify the address and ownership details associated with a maintenance bill. The AI successfully looked up the account, verified the caller, and provided the requested information.
insights.verbatim: Whose address is on file? ... Who owns the unit?
